    <entry>
      <title>前端导出功能</title>
      <link href="/2022/11/11/%E5%89%8D%E7%AB%AF%E5%AF%BC%E5%87%BA%E5%8A%9F%E8%83%BD/"/>
      <url>/2022/11/11/%E5%89%8D%E7%AB%AF%E5%AF%BC%E5%87%BA%E5%8A%9F%E8%83%BD/</url>
      
        <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h2 id="post请求后端返回文件流"><a href="#post请求后端返回文件流" class="headerlink" title="post请求后端返回文件流"></a>post请求后端返回文件流</h2><details class="folding-tag" blue><summary> 查看内容 </summary>              <div class='content'>              <ol><li><p>post配置请求头</p><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">//请求</span><br><span class="line">service.interceptors.request.use(config =&gt; &#123;</span><br><span class="line">  // 导出接口添加请求头，暂时写死了一个接口</span><br><span class="line">  if (config.url.includes(&#x27;specificAnalysisExcel&#x27;)) &#123;</span><br><span class="line">    config.responseType = &#x27;blob&#x27;; //请求加上responseType</span><br><span class="line">  &#125;</span><br><span class="line">  return config;</span><br><span class="line">&#125;);</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><blockquote><p>如果出现导出文件打开失败就是请求头问题</p></blockquote></li><li><p>导出方法</p><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br><span class="line">15</span><br><span class="line">16</span><br><span class="line">17</span><br><span class="line">18</span><br><span class="line">19</span><br><span class="line">20</span><br><span class="line">21</span><br><span class="line">22</span><br><span class="line">23</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">async exportExcel() &#123;</span><br><span class="line">      let res = await &#x27;接口&#x27;;</span><br><span class="line">      if (!res) &#123;</span><br><span class="line">        return;</span><br><span class="line">      &#125;</span><br><span class="line">      const blob = new Blob([res]);</span><br><span class="line">      let url = window.URL.createObjectURL(blob);</span><br><span class="line">      if (&quot;download&quot; in document.createElement(&quot;a&quot;)) &#123;</span><br><span class="line">        try &#123;</span><br><span class="line">          let link = document.createElement(&quot;a&quot;);</span><br><span class="line">          link.style.display = &quot;none&quot;;</span><br><span class="line">          link.href = url;</span><br><span class="line">          link.setAttribute(&quot;download&quot;, &quot;自定义文件名称.xls&quot;);</span><br><span class="line">          document.body.appendChild(link);</span><br><span class="line">          link.click();</span><br><span class="line">          link.remove();</span><br><span class="line">        &#125; catch (e) &#123;</span><br><span class="line">          console.log(e);</span><br><span class="line">        &#125;</span><br><span class="line">      &#125; else &#123;</span><br><span class="line">        navigator.msSaveBlob(blob, &quot;自定义文件名称.xls&quot;);</span><br><span class="line">      &#125;</span><br><span class="line">    &#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li></ol>              </div>            </details>]]></content>
      
      
